As a pro athlete for over a decade you inevitably learn the importance of nutrition. It’s drilled into you one way or another. But as a kid, well, that’s really something you just do not care about. And nowwww, as a dad, I can’t help but make that a priority for my daughter. 1 in 8 kids go to school hungry. 1 in 8! School can be tough but when you’re hungry, it’s A LOT tougher. It makes kids more likely to feel down and struggle in the classroom. That’s why I’m excited to partner up with @drinkorgain and @foodcorps this month to help fuel growing minds and give kids access to proper nutrition. Orgain is making a $5 donation for every post using the hashtag #foodforfocus before Sept. 30 - and I encourage you to join in!  #orgainpartner
